entries.description:
If you want to learn Python there are a variety of ways to go about it.  MIT's Intro to Computer Science Using Python is one way that deserves consideration. The course will teach you a variety of computer science concepts and give you the foundation of computer science that you need to pursue whatever is bringing you into programming.
